title: Hot Dog on a Stick with Paul F. Tompkins
itunes:title: Hot Dog on a Stick with Paul F. Tompkins
description:
Paul F. Tompkins (Threedom, The Neighborhood Listen, Stay F. Homekins) joins the 'boys to discuss summertime go-to's, McDonald's, and Heathcliff comics before a review of Hot Dog on a Stick. Plus, another edition of Slop Quiz.
